# Copy to .env.production (local, gitignored) or set in Vercel → Environment Variables.
#
# HTTPS sites (e.g. Vercel) require wss://. Browsers block ws:// from an https:// page
# (mixed content).
#
# Use the full WebSocket URL including path (nginx often proxies /ws):
VITE_SIGNALING_URL=wss://your-domain.com/ws
#
# If you set only the origin (e.g. wss://your-domain.com), the client appends /ws automatically.
